headline: Archer Roose Wines Now Available to Pop and Pour on Princess Cruises
summary: Archer Roose Wines, the fast-growing canned wine brand, is now available fleetwide on Princess Cruises as its first official canned wine partner. Shipboard guests will enjoy perfect pours of Archer Roose Wines' Bubbly, Pinot Noir, Rosé and Sauvignon Blanc varietals on all voyages starting this September – whether poolside, on excursions, in casinos, via Princess' Ocean Now® and in-room delivery, at Princess Cay or at its Alaska lodges.
